6 and apply to offenses committed on or after that date. Part VIII of this act becomes effective
7 December 1, 2025, and applies to offenses committed, sentences imposed, and any other orders
8 of imprisonment issued on or after that date. The remainder of this act is effective when it
9 becomes law.
